**index.html**
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>My Blog Page</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Welcome to My Blog</h1>
  </header>
  <main class="grid">
    <!-- Blog Post Card Template -->
    <!-- Repeat this 12 times or dynamically generate -->
    <div class="card" onclick="openPost('https://example.com/post1')">
      <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x200" alt="Blog Image" />
      <h2>Post Title 1</h2>
      <p>May 24, 2025</p>
      <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dQw4w9WgXcQ" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </div>

    <!-- Add 11 more cards similarly -->

  </main>
  <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
```

**style.css**
```css
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  background: #f4f4f4;
  color: #333;
}

header {
  background: #222;
  color: white;
  padding: 1em;
  text-align: center;
}

.grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: 1rem;
  padding: 1rem;
}

.card {
  background: white;
  border-radius: 8px;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: transform 0.2s;
}

.card:hover {
  transform: scale(1.02);
}

.card img {
  width: 100%;
  height: auto;
  display: block;
}

.card h2 {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  margin: 0.5rem;
}

.card p {
  margin: 0.5rem;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: #666;
}

.card iframe {
  width: 100%;
  height: 200px;
  border: none;
}
```

**script.js**
```javascript
function openPost(url) {
  window.open(url, '_blank');
}
